9 (A) A LOCAL BOARD SHALL PROVIDE LANGUAGE–RELATED ASSISTANCE
10 AND MATERIALS IN VOTING AND ELECTIONS TO VOTERS WHO HAVE LIMITED
11 ENGLISH PROFICIENCY IN EACH LANGUAGE DESIGNATED BY THE STATE BOARD
