1 (D) (1) MATERIALS PROVIDED IN A DESIGNATED LANGUAGE SHALL:
2 (I) BE OF AN EQUAL QUALITY TO THE CORRESPONDING
3 ENGLISH LANGUAGE MATERIALS; AND
